packed layout record Word:
  value: u16

layout write into view gives i32:
  let bytes be buffer of 4 u8 filled with 0
  let window be view of bytes from 1 for 2
  let word be Word with value be 258
  write word into window at 0
  (bytes at 1 as i32) plus ((bytes at 2 as i32) times 10)

main gives i32:
  layout write into view
